editorialNotes.standard: Once again, the creators of The Human Body and Simple Machines have turned playtime into a rich learning experience. Tinybopâs sandbox-style app lets kids experiment to their heartsâ contentâseeing what happens when they move the sun, whip up winds, and cause rainstorms. editorialNotes.standard: An utterly charming way to introduce young kids to music and animation, Loopimal is simple and powerful in a way that almost defies description. Kids arrange and rearrange tiles in sequences underneath a cute polar bear, octopus, and the like, triggering a series of musical tones mirrored by adorable dances from the animal gang. There are no goals and no consequencesâjust a safe place to learn, play, and laugh.
